Extrudes by a given amount.



```js
extrude(length: number, sketch_group_set: SketchGroupSet) -> ExtrudeGroupSet
```

### Examples

```js
const example = startSketchOn('-XZ')
  |> startProfileAt([0, 0], %)
  |> line([10, 0], %)
  |> arc({
       angle_end: 0,
       angle_start: 120,
       radius: 5
     }, %)
  |> line([5, 0], %)
  |> line([0, 10], %)
  |> bezierCurve({
       control1: [-10, 0],
       control2: [2, 10],
       to: [-5, 10]
     }, %)
  |> line([-5, -2], %)
  |> close(%)
  |> extrude(10, %)
```
